    <string name="historyText">This area is for you to list your medical history, conditions, and allergies along with any details such as dates and names. 
    </string>
    
    <string name="medicationsText">This area is for you to list your prescription and non-prescription medications, as well as dietary supplements.  You should include details such as dosages and how frequently you take the medication. 
    </string>
    
    <string name="temperatureText">This area is for you to track your body temperature.        
    </string>
    
    <string name="weightsText">This area is for you track your weight.  The BMI will automatically be calculated from the height and weight that you enter.
    </string>
    
    <string name="bloodpressureText">This area is for you track your blood pressure and pulse.
    </string>
    
    <string name="bloodsugarText">This area is for you track your blood glucose readings, along with details of your meals, and any notes you may need to make.
    </string>
    
    <string name="testText">This area is for you track the results of your medical tests, lab tests, and any other results that you want to maintain.
    </string>
    
    <string name="visitsText">This area is for you to track your office visits, who you met, what happened, and more.
    </string>
    
    <string name="officesText">This area is for you to record details about medical offices, such as hours, who to call, and more.
    </string>
        
    <string name="dbadminText">This area includes database administration functions such as resetting the database, importing and exporting data to a text file,
    etc.  Please be careful with some of these functions as they can wipe out your saved data. 
    </string>
    
    <string name="documentsText">This area is for you to keep track of files and documents such as lab reports.  You can either include files that are on your device
        or use your camera to take a photo of the document if this device has a camera. 
    </string>
    
